COMPUTER REPAIR: Diagnosing and fixing computer hardware

Category: Electrical
Base skill: 35% (+5%/level, cap 98%)

Diagnosing and repairing broken computer hardware. Distinct from
Computer Operation (using a computer) and Computer Programming
(writing software) - this is fixing the machine itself.

NOTES:
  No AetherMUD command currently rolls this skill directly. It is
  available for character concept and staff-adjudicated roleplay.

